snippet.title: Stikbold! Launch Trailer | Steam, PS4 & Xbox One
snippet.description:
Stikbold! is a groovy 70s-themed single and local multiplayer fantasy dodgeball game with intense, quirky arenas and chaos-inducing random events which change the outcome of each round.

Out now on Steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/429330/
www.stikbold.com

Coming to PS4 on April 5th & Xbox One April 8th
